description: Ambulance crew members say they are willing to return to work under the leadership of Mel Walden.
title: Alderney ambulance staff offer to return to work after dispute
title_page: Alderney ambulance staff offer to return to work after dispute - BBC News
maintext: He said there had been a crisis and there are things to resolve, but "we now have an opportunity to think clearly about the type of service we want going forward".
